{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "團結就是奢望", "storyInfo": "費斯特等人組織自救軍撤離。同時，雖然羅德島對於“灰禮帽”並不完全信任，但也只能與他合作。變形者集群向戈爾丁展現了殘酷的真相。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g4_ordnancefactory", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾座軍工廠......都已經空了。", "name": "洛洛"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們搬走了兩條流水線，剩下的都毀了。", "name": "費斯特"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時情況緊急，我們不知道薩卡茲雇傭兵多久會發現軍工廠的動靜，否則工人們能拆走更多設備的。", "name": "費斯特"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海布里區——新工業區的感覺和我在的舊工業區感覺確實不太一樣，這裡......", "name": "洛洛"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在薩迪恩區，我們像是扳手，敲敲打打，想辦法拼湊出一切。而這裡......這些輸送帶......我不知道，或許你們更像是齒輪。", "name": "洛洛"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穩定運轉，晝夜不停。", "name": "洛洛"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經習慣了，人的適應力就是那麼驚人。", "name": "費斯特"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到了，在這裡。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些貨櫃上刻著符號？這是？", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們工作室流傳的暗語，是當年大家約著偷懶的時候用的，沒想到現在派上了用場。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來想盡辦法喘口氣這一點，倒是哪個區的工人都一樣。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看看，帕特他們聚攏了大部分其他區被打散的自救軍成員。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海布里區的安全屋雖然也被襲擊了，但是地塊更深處的幾條被當做休息站的管道還沒有被發現。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們應該就在那裡。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drone", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我回來了~", "name": "洛克十八"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "附近薩卡茲崗哨的位置已經標記出來了。他們的人不多，看來城裡的兵力要不然上了前線，要不然就追著其他人去了。", "name": "洛克十八"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可露希爾小姐，我還是不覺得在無人機上搭載你的語音庫是個好主意。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這架無人機的升級我可也是幫了忙的！", "name": "洛克十八"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，不說廢話了。剛才阿斯卡綸來了消息，我們的部分通訊系統有可能被維多利亞的哪個大公爵入侵了。", "name": "洛克十八"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不相信他們能入侵到底層啦，但是以防萬一，我需要再做一遍全面檢查。", "name": "洛克十八"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特，會合地點的位置確認了嗎？", "name": "洛克十八"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經確認了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好，我瞧瞧......", "name": "洛克十八"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們雖然有閃靈這個超級保鑣，但她還需要照顧傷患們。所以，避免一切戰鬥，明白了嗎？", "name": "洛克十八"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞭解。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們先去和剩下的自救軍接觸，我和克洛維希婭馬上開始組織轉移——", "name": "洛克十八"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_424_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，洛洛。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？嗯。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，沒什麼......", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我在想，海布里區平時有這麼安靜嗎？", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空氣中的溫度......附近甚至沒有鍛造爐在工作。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是個好兆頭，我們得加快行動。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g5_ordnancefactory_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從這裡的檢修管道，應該就能進入深層的......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.4, "channel": "w", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "w", "fadetime": 0.8}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_unsheathe", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 8.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰！", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特，是我！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "湯米！你來了！", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該在下面等我們，薩卡茲的軍隊剛清剿過安全屋，上面可能還有巡邏的小隊。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我知道，我們的損失不算輕，戴的手臂斷了，凱瑟琳給他做了下應急處理。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們剩下的人還有多久才到？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們應該已經出發了，放心，隨隊的有專業醫生，她會接好戴的手臂的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，好的。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的人都聚在K13檢修通道的下層。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說......自救軍要撤出倫蒂尼姆？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是暫時的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還會回來，湯米，我們是倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，傷患們需要一個安全的地方，而倫蒂尼姆城內......無處落腳。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道了。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快點下去吧，凱瑟琳嘴上不說，但我們都看得出來，她很擔心你。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽說諾伯特區的事情了嗎？天哪，那個地塊被薩卡茲直接扔出城了！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說，那個會飛的要塞還摧毀了大公爵們的高速軍艦......那可是一艘高速軍艦！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭爆發了，費斯特，可我從沒真正經歷過......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我之前還以為，加入自救軍不過是和以前一樣，站在輸送帶前擰螺絲。只不過這次武器是交付給你們的而已。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們......這裡是我們的家。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，倫蒂尼姆是我們的家。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只屬於這裡，對吧。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g11_victoriaroom_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我想，我已經表現出足夠的誠意了。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不算出人意料，我們也早就注意到了薩卡茲的秘密交通網。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但確實有一些值得確認的細節，我們會針對這些地方進行進一步的調查。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其中的一些節點......我能猜到背後是誰。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有關後續調查的結果，希望我們也能共享。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，就和我之前承諾的一樣。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島的反應很快，你們的終端信號已經重新加密了。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有機會，我倒真的很想認識一下那位可露希爾工程師。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她一定不喜歡你。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貴司真是一家人才濟濟的製藥企業。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，公爵閣下從來不介意自己多一些朋友，少一些敵人。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況，公爵閣下畢竟是亞歷山德莉娜的血親，她十分願意愛護自己的這位晚輩。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，務必替我感謝她的關照。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下，我出於尊敬仍願意這麼稱呼你，但這並不代表我的任何立場。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以選擇叫我推進之王。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞是一副沉重的擔子，亞歷山德莉娜殿下，它遠不如表面那般光鮮。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "某個人——無論她是誰，自稱什麼，某個人的歸來對這個國家毫無裨益。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在某些特定的情況下，如果那個人不恰當地運用了她的身份和影響力，甚至可能有害。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我個人的見解。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就藏好你個人的見解。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道，我如今願意暫且和你和平相處，不是因為想聽你那些陳腔濫調。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下，我們之間沒必要這麼針鋒相對，我不過是個聽命辦事的，在職權範圍內我也已經表達了我的善意。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許是你表達得太隱晦了，要不就是我們對善意的定義有所不同。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提出讓各位前往諾伯特區不算嗎？你在那裡應該有位被困的朋友。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為，你能感受到——我很願意站在你的立場上推進我們的合作，我在送你人情。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的目標是拿到結構圖，其餘的行動可以由各位自行定奪，包括救援你的那位朋友。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若你願意直接用你手上的那把劍交換，我甚至可以考慮不辭辛勞，親自幫忙。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收起你的那份噁心的假仁假義。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽好了，我不想琢磨你和你背後的公爵在打什麼主意，又在算計什麼事情。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滾遠點，別擋我的路。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並且給我牢牢記住，阿勒黛的帳，我和你，和你的主子還有得算。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說到做到。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛收到聯絡，公爵閣下的特別反應小組已經為各位做好了撤離倫蒂尼姆並登上諾伯特區的準備。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，出發吧。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“灰禮帽”先生，在我第一次見到你的時候，在我瞭解到公爵閣下對羅德島的資訊掌握到如此程度的時候，我就在想......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，你們一直都做得到，對嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你指什麼？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是我們，還是薩卡茲，乃至自救軍的行動，你們從來不是一無所知。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也並不像各位想像的那般簡單，那般完整。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲，特別是王庭中的某些人就算對我們來說也很棘手，我有很多同事因此喪命。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你們自始至終都牢牢把握著事情的走向。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們......尤其是你們背後那些維多利亞的大公爵們，為什麼要放任事態發展到這種地步？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位卡茲戴爾的攝政王是個了不起的對手，我想，這一點連老威靈頓都會承認。卡茲戴爾軍事委員會的那些技術與裝備也讓人印象深刻。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種誇讚由一位維多利亞大公爵意志的代行者說出，未免也太像句諷刺了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據我們的分析，特雷西斯的實力確實很強大，但是遠不該讓維多利亞陷入如此被動的境地。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我明白了，你們只是選擇袖手旁觀。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#20$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們眼睜睜看著自己的國家陷入戰火。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#20$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，羅德島的小小領導人，你多大？十五歲還是十六歲？你甚至還只是個孩子。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們痛恨鮮血，你們痛恨戰爭。但我要說明一點，我們也沒那麼喜歡這些東西。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但對於我們，戰爭的目的永遠不是它本身，戰爭是政治的延伸，薩卡茲們需要用一場戰爭團結自己，維多利亞未必不需要。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只不過，團結在誰的周圍值得探討。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅僅為了這一點，你們就——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#20$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一點很重要，比你想的重要得多。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭是殘酷的，它會帶來傷害，帶來死亡，它會讓我們以最赤裸裸的樣子暴露在彼此面前，它會扯下所有偽裝。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在歷史行進的某些階段，我們需要這種坦誠。每個人都需要。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做好準備吧，羅德島的各位，我們該啟程了。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "channel": "n", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "n", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉！你也被他們抓來了？！", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊托，她只是個普通的老師，學校裡的孩子仍需要人照顧。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經摧毀了你想摧毀的，你還想牽連多少人？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您來了，閣下。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女妖又找上我們了，找上了我們其中之一。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這就命令部隊前去支援。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用，與他散散步也不錯。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去找老紅眼病吧，他正開了瓶好酒等著你，我們已經厭煩聽他嘮叨那些陳年舊事了。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是個比我們更好的聽眾。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——我明白了，那麼容我告退。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁從沒感覺到自己的喉嚨如此乾澀。眼前的人與她記憶中的茉莉別無二致，連最細微的小動作都一模一樣。"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她總微微皺起眉頭，關注著頑皮孩子們的一舉一動，她會在晚餐時分端上麵包，輕輕斥責沒有洗手的人。"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她仍是那副表情，可為什麼......"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁後背的汗水浸透了衣裳。"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蘭西的拇指昨天又擦傷了，放心，我給他塗好藥啦。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他總是這麼讓人操心。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是......什麼......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位老師已經回到了學校，她能照看好那些孩子的。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聊聊天怎麼樣？", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放鬆點，不過是場閒談，如果你還是感到不舒服，我們也可以繼續用這張臉主人的身份與您相處，戈爾丁女士。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許先聊聊天氣啦，聊聊孩子們的學業？還有那場戲，戈爾丁女士，現在想起來我都忍不住要掉淚。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一眨眼，孩子們都長得這麼大了。", "name": "“茉莉”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 8.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了，別再用茉莉的語氣和我說話！別再頂著那張臉！你這怪物！", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#3$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底......想幹什麼？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#3$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要喝茶嗎？萊托的品味不錯，他這裡的茶葉相當美味。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特雷西斯委派的那些任務也算有個交代啦，接下來，我們可以稍微休息一下。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你在我身邊多久了？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒你想像的那麼久，不過，我們能不能跳過那些無聊的工作話題？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在是休息時間，我們想做點自己真正感興趣的事。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如——", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽一聽你對這個時代的想法，聽一聽你對這一切的結論。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#10$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不明白。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......你們借助我毀了自救軍，我對你們已經沒有利用價值了。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#3$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......該死！我親手交出了這一切......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#3$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼自責，戈爾丁，這沒什麼大不了的，我們有千萬種辦法拿到自救軍據點的位置，你不是唯一的情報源。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也許有點傷人，你甚至不是稱得上重要的一個。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們對你這個人確實有些小小的興趣，我們很享受看你的那些作品，以及和你本人聊天。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，陪我們聊聊吧，這沒什麼深意，只是閒談。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的閒談我們已經發起過無數次，用無數的身份，與無數的人進行過。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我們依然很困惑，我們還是不願放棄任何一次可能得出答案的機會。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁女士，你覺得——", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#10$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們應該如何生活？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#10$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}